description: Belarusian media figures tell the BBC how their lives have been turned upside down during the protests.
title: Belarus protests: 'There's no way back. The people will not forgive this'
title_page: Belarus protests: 'There's no way back. The people will not forgive this' - BBC News
maintext: "He started telling me what a wonderful country we live in and asking what I thought I was doing. He said he was warning me nicely, but that other people would come tomorrow," she explained from Ukraine, where she is now staying for safety.
